<div id="contact" class="flexbox vertical center"> 
  <div class="page-header flexbox vertical center">
    <div class="inner flexbox vertical flex-1">
      <div class="flexbox horizontal center flex-1">
        <div class="title flexbox vertical start">
          <div class="line-a">
            Contact AnyKey
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-section flexbox vertical stretch flex-1">
    <div class="inner flexbox vertical stretch">
      <div class="headline">
        Questions? Suggestions?<br>Reach out to us directly
      </div>
      <div class="flexbox horizontal center wrap justify-space-around">      
        <div class="intro-section">
          <p>Our team is excited to promote and grow diverse communities in competitive gaming.</p>
          <p>We would be happy to answer questions about tournaments, research, and our initiatives. Inquires from members of the press, industry, and academia are all encouraged equally.</p>
